title: **Ibiza live mix from Base Bar 2 Inc. Hed Kandi**
description:
Recorded live from the White Isles trendiest bar, Hed Kandi put on their first event of the Summer. The music, mixing and quality is there in abundance.
CD.1 Hed Kandi Live
CD.2 DJ Yoshi & Mikael
CD.3 DJ James Scott

Three completely contrasting styles & music all recorded live. Remember these mixes have been nowhere near a studio and will never be released elsewhere.

Party People Enjoy & Please, Please Seed!
Leave feedback, if you can.
